OL,3,CTown ban on ice cream vans within 100m
OL,4,Cof schools
OL,6,FIce cream vans will be banned from
OL,7,Ftrading within 100 metres of schools
OL,8,Fin Barnsley under new rules introduced
OL,9,Fby the council.
OL,11,FChanges to street trading rules are
OL,12,Fset to be approved by Barnsley
OL,13,FCouncil's cabinet at their next
OL,14,Fmeeting on 11 June, according to the
OL,15,FLocal Democracy Reporting Service.
