OL,3,CTown ban on ice cream vans within 100m
OL,4,Cof schools
OL,6,FThe changes mean mobile traders ` such
OL,7,Fas ice cream vans ` will not be
OL,8,Fallowed to remain in place for more
OL,9,Fthan 20 minutes, and must not stop
OL,10,Fwithin 100m of the main entrance to
OL,11,Fschools, "without written consent".
OL,13,FMobile traders will also be banned
OL,14,Ffrom Barnsley town centre. Businesses
OL,15,Fwhose food hygiene rating falls below
OL,16,Fa three will have their street trading
OL,17,Fconsent suspended.
OL,19,FDBS checks will also be required by
OL,20,FBarnsley Council when traders apply
OL,21,Ffor a street trading licence.
