OL,6,FThe new policy states: "Mobile traders
OL,7,Fmust move from position to position
OL,8,Fremaining stationary for no longer
OL,9,Fthan 20 minutes to initially attract
OL,10,Fcustomers and thereafter only long
OL,11,Fenough to serve customers present.
OL,13,F"The vehicle must move on as soon as
OL,14,Fthe last customer has been served and
OL,15,Fno other customer is clearly awaiting
OL,16,Fservice."
